    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_2028398258014512501.png",
                "id": "talent87193",
                "key": "Dance of Samser",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dance of Samser"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, if the party includes <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro Characters</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro Characters</span> and characters from no other Elements, create 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Golden Chalice's Bounty</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Golden Chalice's Bounty</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After opponent's characters are affected by the Bloom reaction: </span>Your team no longer generates <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>, but instead summons <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bountiful Cores</span>.</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/c82a120ef3389c55999b6069de0c8ddc_9090000124016199759.png",
                "id": "talent64453",
                "key": "Dance of Haftkarsvar",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dance of Haftkarsvar"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. The target character receives <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lingering Aeon</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Lingering Aeon</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase: </span>Deal 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> to affected character.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/e701a5d9dee57abe1f108242af52b000_1127859871653331421.png",
                "id": "talent11932",
                "key": "Dance of Abzendegi: Distant Dreams, Listening Spring",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dance of Abzendegi: Distant Dreams, Listening Spring"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you declare the end of your Round: </span>If this summon has at least 2 Usages remaining, deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>. (Consumes <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span>)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack, Max 3 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/20/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7023879873887858860.png",
                "id": "talent82091",
                "key": "Bountiful Core",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/20/35428890/ded0956520d3dce12af6dfcbdfab5d01_4001117127882432411.png",
                "title": "Bountiful Core"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/20/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_811090395483213013.png",
                "id": "talent13990",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro/Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/20/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_5230063656855637076.png",
                "id": "talent8145",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/20/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1387824794691787895.png",
                "id": "talent70606",
